Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.67,0:24:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1440673,1443208}Sunday, May 21.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.20,0:24:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1443208,1448314}Paris is full of life, and the faces of people\Nare brightened by long-forgotten smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.04,0:24:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1449048,1453118}Between one fight and another, the streets\Nof the city host lively dance parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.88,0:24:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1453886,1457089}Fireworks explode against\Na clear blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.08,0:24:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1457089,1459792}For the first time in a long time,\Nthe people of Paris enjoy alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.79,0:24:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1460793,1462528}However…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.52,0:24:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1462528,1464363}Next time on "Isabelle from Paris":
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.36,0:24:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1464363,1467299}"Midday Dance Party".\NPlease look forward to it.
